{"tid":705744,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好好珍惜你中學既兄弟","createTime":"2018-06-17T12:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T03:05:37.000Z","uid":98190,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"217c491e0030dbe3475895ad4577632fb300133e","tid":705744,"uid":98190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T12:22:07.000Z","msg":"自己係大學入面打滾左幾年，識咗唔少人<br />\n大部分都只係hi bye，只可玩樂，極其量都係談心。<br />\n當你有難，唔開心既時候，只有好少會伸出援手，其他只會不聞不問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己既女朋友，原本以為係我既所有，未來。但原來可以話散就散，話走就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唯有中學玩開班兄弟，係你唔開心嗰時同你出去玩，開心既時候一齊分享，無聊既時候同你打機。有爭執，鬧交嗰時，打場波，講句屌你老母就無事。到我之前真係有事，成班友仔二話不說，真係出黎幫我。自己返屋企都眼濕濕，好感激佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除咗自己老豆老母，希望大家好好珍惜大家中學識既朋友，可能係你永遠既真心朋友<br />\n<br />\n兄弟們，謝謝你！"},{"pid":"01db812802117dd4d806f4635689387bd5fc111b","tid":705744,"uid":188049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T12:44:42.000Z","msg":"我啲兄弟都唔在意自己可以點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5a60faa40fabc37778678a9917471d4b13c750","tid":705744,"uid":98190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01db812802117dd4d806f4635689387bd5fc111b","tid":705744,"uid":188049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T12:44:42.000Z","msg":"我啲兄弟都唔在意自己可以點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T15:54:02.000Z","msg":"主動啲同佢地分享吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52261364784ae442443a4e44f56db17bc12b68e7","tid":705744,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de5a60faa40fabc37778678a9917471d4b13c750","tid":705744,"uid":98190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01db812802117dd4d806f4635689387bd5fc111b","tid":705744,"uid":188049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T12:44:42.000Z","msg":"我啲兄弟都唔在意自己可以點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T15:54:02.000Z","msg":"主動啲同佢地分享吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:05:37.000Z","msg":"會攰"}]}